  "text": "Here, we present the first genome-scale model reconstruction and analysis of Zygosaccharomyces parabailii, which is one of the 3 species described in the Z. bailii sensu lato clade and one of the 12 formally described species in the Zygosaccharomyces genus [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
